snippet.title: Bonkheads gameplay (PC Game, 1998)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Bonkheads, PC game produced by 1 AM Entertainment in 1998 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/bonkheads/5316/
Few stages in one player mode. Game reminds first Mario games and Donkey Kong, it's a good casual game.
Played through emulated Windows (Win 98/Win XP) virtual machine.
Recorded with original sound.
